data.description: Amazing contemporary Central Park home on a rare oversized Central Park lot--this is the one you've been waiting for!  Gorgeous interior with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, beautiful cabinets, an open layout, high ceilings, tons of light, a spacious primary retreat with a walk-in closet/private balcony/en suite bathroom, 2 additional bedrooms and another bathroom on the second level, main level laundry, a great finished basement with flex space and an additional bedroom/bathroom, and more.  While most homes in Central Park have smaller yards, this one has a rare extra large landscaped yard, a stamped concrete patio, dog run, and an extra wide 2.5 car garage with plenty of room for storage.  Fully owned solar panels provide clean energy without paying a monthly lease or loan!  Fantastic location close to Bluff Lake Nature Center wildlife refuge, the restaurants and shops at Eastbridge Town Center and Central Park Town Center, the incredible Stanley Market food hall, King Soopers for groceries, the Moorhead Rec Center, community pools, the CU Anschutz hospital campus, and so much more!  Showings begin April 11th.  Buyer to verify all information.
